description:
Hairstylist Orlando Pita has ruled the industry for the past 25 years. Now he gets real about work ethic, the show that changed his career, and why beauty editors are terrified of him. Plus: The week in beauty biz (special Kat Von D vs. Jeffree Star edition!), the girls get buzzed with cannabis beauty products, and the new "breathable" nail polish.
